</td>
<td class="item-name q2"><a href="http://www.topwow.top/item-3456.html" class="item_info" id="3456" target="_blank">狗哨</a></td>
</tr>
</table></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wowdb60static.wow-classic.com/uploads/64710301-18c4-45cf-a3a2-73d6d49b509d.jpg" title="狗哨" alt="狗哨" width="" height="" /></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><strong>使用：</strong>召唤1头追踪犬为你作战，持续10分钟。</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><strong>获取方法：</strong><a href="http://www.topwow.top/zone-796.html" title="血色修道院" target="_blank" title="血色修道院">血色修道院</a>的<a href="http://www.topwow.top/npc-3974.html" title="驯犬者洛克希" target="_blank" title="驯犬者洛克希">驯犬者洛克希</a>掉落。虽然攻击力很微弱，不过这种血色豺狗的叫声确实让人觉得恶心，野外pvp有那么些微弱的干扰效果吧。</p><h3 style="white-space: normal;">五、巴罗夫管家铃</h3><p style="white-space: normal;"><table class="item">
